public class InterfaceDescriptionProvider
extends org.eclipse.jface.viewers.LabelProvider
implements org.eclipse.wst.common.ui.internal.search.dialogs.IComponentDescriptionProvider

This is a wrapper over IInterfaceHandler and provides Description of the IInterfaceHandler that it wraps. Its used by InterfaceHandler. This is also a label provider.
